title: Chelsea 8-0 Noah: Ruthless Blues stay perfect after first-half rout

title: Manchester United 2-0 PAOK: Brilliant Amad earns hosts first Europa League win
description: Amad Diallo scored twice as Manchester United finally earned a maiden victory in the Europa League this season with a 2-0 triumph over PAOK.
